Layered Addenda
----------------------------------------------------------------------

The following three addenda apply to BOTH license tracks above and take
precedence over any conflicting clause in either track.

### A. Anti-Bypassing / API-Encapsulation Clause

You may not, directly or indirectly:

(a) wrap, proxy, repackage, or otherwise mediate the Software's APIs,
    binaries, model interfaces, or runtime endpoints in order to provide
    third parties with substantially the Software's functionality while
    avoiding the obligations of either license track above;

(b) operate a managed service, software-as-a-service, platform-as-a-
    service, or any equivalent network-accessible offering whose
    user-facing capabilities are materially derived from the Software,
    without first obtaining a commercial license under section (2);

(c) strip, obscure, or relocate the in-product "About / 关于" panel,
    the contact email displayed at the top of that panel, or the
    integrity-protected About module shipped in
    ``backend/src/governance/about.py``. Removal, masking, or programmatic
    suppression of these surfaces is a license violation regardless of
    the consent of intermediate distributors.

### B. Patent Retaliation Clause

If you (or any affiliate or party acting on your behalf) initiate, fund,
join, or otherwise materially assist a patent infringement claim,
declaratory judgment action, or similar proceeding ("Patent Action")
against any contributor to the Software, or against any user of the
Software based on their use of the Software, then all licenses granted to
you under both license tracks above terminate automatically on the date
the Patent Action is filed. This clause survives termination.

### C. Trademark Reservation

"OctoAgent", "OctoSys", "OctopusAgent", the project logo, and any
confusingly similar marks (collectively the "Marks") are NOT licensed
under either license track. The Marks remain the exclusive property of
